plus_succ.formula: forall M N K, plus M N K -> plus M (s N) (s K)
SigmaFormula: Define nat : nat -> prop by nat zero ; nat (succ N) := nat N

plus_comm.formula: forall M N K, nat K -> plus M N K -> plus N M K
SigmaFormula: Define nat : nat -> prop by nat zero ; nat (succ N) := nat N

lemmas.name: plus_zero

SigmaFormula: Define nat : nat -> prop by nat z; nat (s N) := nat N
Define plus : nat -> nat -> nat -> prop by plus z N N ; plus (s M) N (s K) := plus M N K
